93
00:08:11,410 --> 00:08:13,410
Where is she?

94
00:08:13,960 --> 00:08:18,760
Dad, did you bring me here from the airport

95
00:08:18,760 --> 00:08:21,742
to welcome Kanghan?

96
00:08:22,900 --> 00:08:26,740
You've been mooching off my dad. And now, you want your daughter to join you?

97
00:08:26,740 --> 00:08:28,645
Don't worry.

98
00:08:28,645 --> 00:08:32,340
