162
00:13:48,920 --> 00:13:52,940
Is she in some corner of the mall?

163
00:13:52,940 --> 00:13:59,660
Khun Saya's secretary told me so.

164
00:14:00,420 --> 00:14:03,060
She lied before we met.

165
00:14:04,778 --> 00:14:08,364
Khun Sira, please calm down. Think of Ms. Chairwoman,

166
00:14:08,364 --> 00:14:14,540
because Ms. Chairwoman wanted you to meet Khun Saya.

167
00:14:20,880 --> 00:14:26,020
How about this? You can handle some work while you wait.

168
00:14:26,020 --> 00:14:29,200
Khun Saya will be here any minute.

169
00:14:33,725 --> 00:14:36,670
I'll wait for Khun Saya there.

170
00:14:36,670 --> 00:14:38,630
I'll leave you alone.

171
00:14:41,880 --> 00:14:44,040
Come on.

172
00:14:47,412 --> 00:14:52,112
If he's not here in 15 minutes, I'll leave.

173
00:15:03,820 --> 00:15:06,260
Hello, Khun Sira.

174
00:15:11,720 --> 00:15:14,000
That's her. Khun Saya.

175
00:15:19,065 --> 00:15:21,118
Hello.

176
00:15:21,118 --> 00:15:26,920
Your secretary told my secretary that you had been here for a long time.

177
00:15:26,920 --> 00:15:30,450
It's true. I went to the bathroom.

178
00:15:30,450 --> 00:15:32,930
I'm sorry.

179
00:15:32,933 --> 00:15:35,519
- Please sit down.
- Sure.

180
00:15:43,440 --> 00:15:47,580
Are you angry that I made you wait so long?

181
00:15:48,420 --> 00:15:54,140
No. I was working while I was waiting for you.

182
00:15:55,520 --> 00:15:59,212
In that case, I'll let you handle the work.

183
00:16:00,020 --> 00:16:01,672
Okay.

184
00:16:03,700 --> 00:16:05,600
Miss, you can't go in there.

185
00:16:05,600 --> 00:16:08,260
