188
00:16:18,780 --> 00:16:21,029
Do you have an appointment?

189
00:16:21,029 --> 00:16:22,910
I don't need it.

190
00:16:22,910 --> 00:16:25,400
Tell Khun Sira that Chanaratee,

191
00:16:25,400 --> 00:16:33,450
the only daughter of Khun Papop, the CEO of the clothing manufacturing company KKPP, the number one best-selling brand in Thailand, has come to meet him.

192
00:16:34,400 --> 00:16:37,740
Could you repeat that? I couldn't follow you.

193
00:16:39,566 --> 00:16:42,858
I can't tell Mr. Sira about that.

194
00:16:42,858 --> 00:16:46,120
Since you can't tell him, I'll go in myself.

195
00:16:47,120 --> 00:16:51,146
