202
00:17:27,331 --> 00:17:28,839
No.

203
00:17:28,839 --> 00:17:31,240
You must be upset that I was late.

204
00:17:31,240 --> 00:17:34,010
So you're making me weather this out.

205
00:17:34,017 --> 00:17:37,320
It's rude to be late.

206
00:17:38,220 --> 00:17:42,160
But you've apologized, and I've forgiven you.

207
00:17:42,160 --> 00:17:44,080
Is this what you call forgiveness?

208
00:17:44,080 --> 00:17:46,710
Then why are you doing this?

209
00:17:46,713 --> 00:17:51,699
