212
00:17:57,220 --> 00:17:59,600
Khun Sira, I think you're taking me too lightly.

213
00:17:59,600 --> 00:18:02,920
Didn't anyone teach you to be polite?

214
00:18:07,398 --> 00:18:10,110
Khun Saya, I came to see you for two reasons.

215
00:18:10,110 --> 00:18:13,430
First, the chairwoman asked me to come. Second, I respect your father.

216
00:18:13,435 --> 00:18:16,320
