225
00:19:14,180 --> 00:19:15,700
Okay.

226
00:19:15,700 --> 00:19:20,120
Call Rossarin and tell her I'm going back to the office soon.

227
00:19:20,120 --> 00:19:21,998
Yes.

228
00:19:27,160 --> 00:19:29,060
